      "date": "2014-10-15 08:23:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4:\n\nOleg, thanks for correction. - connect fsm move to FULL state import so we may have race with sending vs connect in additional to the re-send vs connecting. in that case we need to be sure all flags set before request may send. \nBut i'm agree http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/11723/4/lustre/ptlrpc/import.c isn't fix all bugs in that area. Looks we need abort a BRW request waiting and execute a brw_redo loop to apply changes in cli->cl_max_pages_per_rpc, and ELC support in case ns_connect_flags was changed for already queued rpc's.",
